  <brief_title>Study of TAP and Laparoscopic and Robotic Gynecologic Procedures and Obese Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of Transversus Abdominis Plane Block in Reducing Immediate Postoperative Pain in Obese Women After Laparoscopic or Robotic Gynecologic Procedures</official_title>
  <sponsors>
